This project is a derivative work based on the reference harness project
by robin (https://github.com/robin/harness), licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

The original work provided the architectural patterns, team structure concepts,
and skill orchestration principles that were extended and evolved in this project.

This project modifies and extends the original work with:
- Automated project context initialization (context/, outputs/, BRIEF.md, etc.)
- Session management system (ROADMAP, BRIEF, HANDOFF)
- Workspace constitution (CLAUDE.md) with context reference rules
- Team architecture templates for 6 architectural patterns

For the original work, see: reference/harness/
